wetteronline.de/robots.txt
#PUPPET#

User-agent: *
Disallow:

0

User-agent refers to the type of web crawler that is allowed to search the document. 
* being the wildcard, inhibiting all web crawlers
Disallow will state any page on the website that is not available for the webcrawler. When nothing is stated, the whole website is open to be 'looked through' 

